{"tid":1471123,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"818 迫 和 理 非 唔 出 黎 劇 本","createTime":"2019-08-14T07:53:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T13:07:57.000Z","uid":192851,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"a03b09fc70b3576e66186c6fd2bdd3ba0dd054a7","tid":1471123,"uid":192851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T07:53:06.000Z","msg":"而家大家都想818勇武休息，希望引最大數目既人出番黎行，keep番住個勢<br />\n<br />\n我係對家就更係臨行之前搞下手腳，唔批遊行就一定，仲可能會拉下女仔，引大家破壞下野咁<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">目的就係令和理非，由其係一家大細嗰，71嗰時喺金鐘唔轉入立法會嗰啲，冇信心行出黎</span><br />\n<br />\n人數少，鬼扮分化撚，鬼扮失敗撚又可以出黎做野<br />\n<br />\n大家小心"},{"pid":"20cebf5098fd6771548fc45d28499060905121a5","tid":1471123,"uid":192851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T07:53:46.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"a03db07f240892aa6ff8c0bc5bb33b921f8e6839","tid":1471123,"uid":192851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T07:54:24.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"9123359bb90354571ebba85b791521cfaf699af4","tid":1471123,"uid":192851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T07:54:53.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"3f908119d9e56a3c56b559c07bf79eb0191bbc20","tid":1471123,"uid":224018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T07:55:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">818 維園見</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f418fd33d0b6f5259b9412a580764b1b7b3819a0","tid":1471123,"uid":171992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T07:55:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/6yR8ycR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6yR8ycR.jpg&h=a587efad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/141044_b70c4022f89dcf56